oads\/2024\/02\/google-ads-library-search-480x233.jpg 480w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 847px, 100vw\" \/><\/p>\n<div id=\"facebook-ads-library\">\ud83d\udea8 Get more insight into how your ads compare to the competition using our latest <a href=\"https:\/\/marketing.localiq.com\/WSLIQContentDLWebsiteGoogleAdsBenchmarks2023.html?cid=Web_WS_incontent_guide_2023benchmarks_Download&amp;utm_source=wordstream&amp;utm_medium=blog&amp;utm_campaign=incontent_links\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">search ad benchmarks report<\/a>!<\/div>\n<h3>6. Facebook Ads Library<\/h3>\n<p>For social media advertising, Facebook offers the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2023\/06\/06\/facebook-ad-library\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Facebook Ads Library<\/a>\u2014which you can consider similar to the Google Transparency Center. This PPC tool also allows anyone to search and filter for information on active ads across the platform.<\/p>\n<p>Use the Facebook Ads Library to identify <a href=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/blog\/ws\/2022\/12\/06\/facebook-advertising-trends\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Facebook advertising trends<\/a>, and get a feel for what you like (or don&#8217;t like) about different <a href=\"https:\/\/localiq.com\/blog\/facebook-ad-examples\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Facebook ad examples<\/a> within your industry. That way, you can create an offensive game plan for how you tailor your ads to <a href=\"https:\/\/localiq.com\/blog\/how-to-make-your-business-stand-out\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">stand out from competitors<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/facebook-ad-library-homepage.png\" alt=\"ppc tools - meta facebook ad library homepage\" width=\"936\" height=\"600\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-72471 size-full\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.wordstream.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/06\/facebook-a